  "texts": [
    "Lavazza and Reichlin (2023) called for the extended scientific community, neuroethicists, and other relevant experts to contribute to the development of this ethical framework, in dialog with society and policymakers (Bassil and Horstkötter, 2023; Capps, 2023).",
    "Creative governance solutions and proactive engagement fostering mutual understanding between scientists and publics will be key.",
    "With prudent guidance, organoids could unlock profound insights into the brain while aligning with deeply held societal values.",
    "With thoughtful guidance, this promising field can progress rapidly within ethical bounds.",
    "Frontiers in Artificial Intelligence 05 frontiersin.org"
  ]
